   500→   * necessary. Compute Host / :authority headers based on 7230#5.7 and 7230#6
   501→   *
   502→   * @param is_connect true if the request has the CONNECT method
   503→   * @param headers the request's headers
   504→   * @return Status representing success or failure. This will fail if there is an invalid url in
   505→   * the request line.
